data.description: Welcome to luxury living in this stunning 4-bedroom, 3 full bathroom condo nestled in a serene community. This brick ranch offers a harmonious blend of elegance and comfort, boasting views of a tranquil pond off your large deck. Step inside to discover an impeccably designed interior featuring 2 spacious main floor bedrooms, and the only unit in the community that offers a loft area that can serve as a home office, custom closet or additional bedroom. Enjoy the convenience of a main floor laundry w/sink and counter space.  The finished basement adds the 4th bedroom & 3rd full bath.   Situated in a sought-after community, this condo offers the convenience of low yard maintenance, paired with the allure of scenic surroundings. Enjoy easy access to nearby amenities, shopping, dining, and entertainment options, ensuring a lifestyle of comfort and convenience. Whether you're seeking a peaceful retreat to call home or an elegant space to entertain guests, this brick ranch condo is sure to exceed your expectations. Come and see all that this beautiful home has to offer!
